## **âœ… 1ï¸âƒ£ JSF + MyBatis ì„¤ì • (`UserBean.java`)**  
ğŸ“Œ **ì…ë ¥í•œ `groupcode`ë¡œ `companyname`ì„ ì¡°íšŒí•˜ëŠ” ë¡œì§ ì¶”ê°€**  

```java
@ManagedBean
@ViewScoped
public class UserBean {
    private String groupcode;
    private String companyname; // ìë™ìœ¼ë¡œ ì±„ì›Œì§ˆ ê°’
    private List<User> pagedList;

    @EJB
    private UserService userService;
    
    public void fetchCompanyName() {
        if (groupcode != null && !groupcode.isEmpty()) {
            companyname = userService.getCompanyNameByGroupcode(groupcode);
        } else {
            companyname = "";
        }
    }

    public void search() {
        pagedList = userService.searchUsersByGroupcode(groupcode);
    }

    // Getter & Setter
}
```

